SELECT * FROM gm_nutrients ORDER BY value DESC;

SELECT * FROM gm_food WHERE category = 'Vegetables' ORDER BY calories DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT name, category, calories, protein FROM gm_food WHERE protein > 10 ORDER BY category, calories ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT f.name, i.source, i.modified_date, i.expiration_date FROM gm_food f JOIN gm_ingredients i ON f.id = i.id WHERE i.expiration_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY i.modified_date DESC;
SELECT n.nutrient_name, n.value, f.name FROM gm_nutrients n JOIN gm_food f ON n.food_id = f.id WHERE n.value > 5 ORDER BY n.value DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT r.food_id, r.rating, r.review_text, f.name FROM gm_reviews r JOIN gm_food f ON r.food_id = f.id WHERE r.rating >= 4.0 ORDER BY r.rating DESC, r.review_text ASC LIMIT 5;
